{"tid":2358483,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"啟德MONACO首批80伙 折實價錢596萬起 呎價2.04萬起","createTime":"2021-01-08T07:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T12:39:50.000Z","uid":144090,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"e01db6e160c09b9303db0e644f0f46e1a3047643","tid":2358483,"uid":144090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:22:14.000Z","msg":"啟德新盤MONACO(MONACO第1期)由會德豐地產發展，MONACO示範單位地址為尖沙咀港威大廈2座9樓，MONACO價單今日已上載，首張價單80伙，折實價錢596萬起，MONACO呎價則由2.04萬元起，料成為2021年頭炮新盤，最快1月中開售首批單位。<br />\n<br />\nMONACO首張價單80伙，首批單位涵蓋第2座住宅的開放式至3房單位，包括14伙開放式、11伙1房、46伙2房及9伙3房單位，面積280至762平方呎，價單定價750.4萬至2,201.6萬元，價單呎價25,619至31,058元。MONACO共4款付款方法，最高折扣20.5%，折實約596萬至約1,750萬元，折實呎價20,368起。<br />\n<br />\n會德豐地產主席梁志堅重申，MONACO屬合理價錢推出市場。 會德豐地產常務董事黃光耀形容MONACO首批單位屬「啟航置業價」。"},{"pid":"25beb2213c12dea00d34c084404f8c1b229186cd","tid":2358483,"uid":144090,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"抵唔抵買"},{"pid":"161dd6d42ee453b365e145b5f1f24d06a58c93ef","tid":2358483,"uid":336070,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"公屋群<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e891c9e9d21d6289d36e1a754a9a37951dc359","tid":2358483,"uid":94467,"like":1,"dislike":46,"score":-45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:05:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/anccch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fanccch&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=30bcac7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/anccch</a><br />\n<br />\n有價單<br />\n想了解可以搵我，滿意回贈"},{"pid":"904b7be23598881c09fdc2435737b668b4662a8b","tid":2358483,"uid":21636,"like":2,"dislike":27,"score":-25,"quote":{"pid":"25beb2213c12dea00d34c084404f8c1b229186cd","tid":2358483,"uid":144090,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"抵唔抵買"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:09:47.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n<br />\n第一批2房1000